data.description: Looking for a Move-in ready house in Round Rock. Welcome to 3426 Shiraz Loop, a beautiful traditional home located in the Sonoma neighborhood! This 3 bedroom and 2 bathroom, 1,918 sq. ft home offers plenty for potential homeowners to be excited about. As you walk in, you’ll be amazed at the attention to detail. The primary bedroom is very spacious featuring a built-in desk. Let’s not forget the covered back patio that will surely be a great spot for evening relaxation. In addition, you’ll find yourself just minutes from Kalahari Resort and easily close to concrete amenities, such as shopping, dining and tolls. This move-in ready, beautifully updated home is close to the Play for All Park, Kalahari, SH130 (easy access to DT, UT, ABIA), IH35, ACC, medical, dining & shopping. Click this link for a beautiful tour: https://portal.solid-photography.com/3426-Shiraz-Loop
